725208f-b.title: Queens: 31st Street - 20th Road
725208f-b.text:
(1)
31st Street, foreground, south of 20th Road (formerly Old Bowery
Bay Road), showing the Peter Rapelje house from 1852-1873.
March 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2 and 3)
The same, viewed westward, from 31st Street and showing also homes
on the west side in the background of 29th Street.
May 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(4)
The same, showing the widening of 31st Street, looking north
from Twenty-first Ave. (Wolcott Street). The site of the house was
at the left where the steam shovel is working.
May 28, 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
